title: by Amazon Sensitive Baby Wipes 1008 Wipes, Unscented, 18 Pack of 56, (Previously a Mama Bear brand, same product)
features: Packaging may vary from images shown. This product was previously a Mama Bear product. Now it’s a part of the by Amazon brand. The product is the exact same formulations, size, quality and the supplier is the same.
MULTI-BENEFIT PACK: 18 packs; 56 water-based wipes per pack
FOR SENSITIVE SKIN: Formulated with mild and gentle ingredients and hypoallergenic for baby's delicate skin
VERSATILE: Suitable for hands, feet and nappy area
SOOTHING INGREDIENTS: Gently cleanses with Aloe Vera
HYPOALLERGENIC: Formulation developed to minimise allergic potential
description: Product Description By Amazon Sensitive Baby Wipes - previously a Mama Bear brand. Formulated with mild and gentle ingredients and hypoallergenic for baby's delicate skin. Suitable for hands, feet and nappy area. Dermatologically approved. Delivered in a case containing 18 packs, with 56 wipes in each pack making a total of 1,008 wipes. Ingredients AQUA, ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE, SODIUM BENZOATE, MYRISTAMIDOPROPYL PG-DIMONIUM CHLORIDE PHOSPHATE, POLYGLYCERYL-4 CAPRATE, HEPTYL GLUCOSIDE, CITRIC ACID, SODIUM GLUCONATE, SODIUM CITRATE Directions Pull back label and remove wipe. Use as required, reseal label after use to keep the wipes moist. Do not flush. Keep wipes and packaging out of the reach of babies and children. Safety Warning Caution: Keep out of reach of children and babies. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If this does occur, rinse well with water. External use only. See more
